-| **MinusMigrator** | Sistema versionado de migra├â┬º├â┬úo de schema com SchemaReader, SQLGenerator, Runner, CLI e GUI | `MinusMigrator_CLI.exe`, `MinusMigrator_GUI.exe`, `MinusMigrator.dll` |
