-### 5.1 Retry com Backoff
-
-```pascal
-type
-  TBackoffPolicy = class abstract
-    function ProximoIntervalo(const ATentativa: Integer): Integer; virtual; abstract;
-  end;
-
-  TExponentialBackoff = class(TBackoffPolicy)
